description:
Watch Psalms Alive with Billy Angel Psalms 46 (Subtitles) on Vision Video 

Director-actor-producer Billy Angel presents a powerful oral interpretation of Psalms 46.

This is an outstanding resource for personal devotions or group worship. In this inspiring video, director-actor-producer Billy Angel presents a powerful oral interpretation of Psalms 46 - God Almighty is with us! in a diverse setting that serves to evoke the mood and ambiance that the original authors intended. Billy’s empathetic presentation honors the ancient Word and carefully places it into the modern context of contemporary life. Primarily based on the King James translation, viewers easily recognize the words of the Psalm while also experiencing its message in a new way.

In this inspiring video, director-actor-producer Billy Angel presents 22 powerful oral interpretations of our favorite Psalms in diverse settings that serve to evoke the mood and ambience that the original authors intended.
